settings.editor: A two-day event for designers with the innovation bug. The gathering will include workshops, fascinating talks, and give-aways that will help you start thinking about the future of design in all fields. Shout out to the ones who want to be those who will change our design future.

settings.description_text: Learn from the best in the field

settings.editor: We have created two days of amazing workshops, inspirational design lectures, and meetings with other creative people for you to connect and learn from. Get tickets and join our growing community of bold designers.
Everyone can be part of this conference - we're going virtual! And we will be streaming it from Los Angeles' grand hall. Buy your tickets today and connect.

settings.title: be part of the future of design
Be part of our community: register for the conference and become part of the Design Cube family.

settings.editor: Design Cube is a community of unique designers who want to be part of the design movement worldwide. They established this conference eight years ago as a mission to grow the design network and really influence today's world.
